snippet.title: Rocket League® - Xbox One Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: The soccer-meets-driving sensation, Rocket League, is coming to Xbox One! Fully optimized for the all-in-one console, the Xbox One version of Rocket League will have all the same features, upgrades, and content found in the PC version, plus several significant additions -- including two Xbox One-exclusive Battle-Cars, the Halo "HogSticker," an alternate version of the Warthog, and the Gears of War "Armadillo!" Releasing February 2016.
